*Počinje* sezonsko ludilo u kupovini (The seasonal shopping frenzy starts).
*Počinje* da se oseća zima (Winter is starting to be felt).
*Počinjali* smo zajedno, ali razdvojili smo se (We started together, but we parted).
*Počeo* je da se oseća miris lekovitog bilja (The smell of medicinal plants started to be felt).
*Počinjao* je da se zagreva (He started to warm up).